channel.description:

It seems to be happening with alot of things i download. Other things its happend with is Buffering YouTube videos and Downloading Moparscape Clients/Sources. or basiclly anything i download.
Now i know this isn't exactly anything atall to do with moparscape but i was wondering if it has something to do with moparscape. It happens with Youtube yes but why it happen with mopar, anyone know why?
Btw dont flame because i know this isn't really about mopar.
